  "text": "Loss-on-ignition (LOI) and water content. The working half-core was sub-sampled at 0.5 cm intervals. Sub-samples were freezedried for at least 24e48 h, depending on water content. LOI was performed on about 0.35 g of dry sediment at 550 C for 5 h following the method of [CITATION_1] ) at 1 cm intervals to determine organic matter (OM) content (Fig. 3) .",
